WEBVTT

00:12.625 --> 00:14.125
Previously on Ray Donovan...

00:15.667 --> 00:16.583
You need to stop seeing my wife.

00:16.667 --> 00:18.750
That's up to her.

00:18.834 --> 00:19.917
Where are the pictures?

00:20.000 --> 00:23.083
Uh, right there, folder.

00:23.166 --> 00:23.333
The other pictures.

00:25.959 --> 00:27.458
ABBY:
Don't you get it?

00:27.542 --> 00:30.250
All I ever wanted was
for you to look at me!

00:30.333 --> 00:32.709
But you can't. You
can't talk to me.

00:32.792 --> 00:34.333
You can't share your pain
with me.

00:34.417 --> 00:35.875
TERRY:
You're the love of my life.

00:35.959 --> 00:37.417
Come to Ireland and marry me.

00:38.625 --> 00:40.542
Hey, Cookie...

00:42.083 --> 00:43.792
(tires screech)

00:43.875 --> 00:46.000
RAY:
You heard the shots,

00:46.083 --> 00:46.917
and then you saw Cookie
walking away.

00:47.000 --> 00:49.458
Marvin?
RAY:
Did he see you?

00:49.542 --> 00:50.166
I don't know.

00:50.250 --> 00:51.041
She should go to the police.

00:51.125 --> 00:52.291
She should tell them
what she saw.

00:52.375 --> 00:55.375
You don't understand
how dangerous this guy is.

00:55.458 --> 00:56.458
He already killed one kid.

00:56.542 --> 00:59.500
How do you know her life
isn't already in danger?!

00:59.583 --> 01:00.583
I'm about to become
the number one

01:00.667 --> 01:03.041
law enforcement officer
in the United States.

01:03.125 --> 01:04.417
Hell, in the fucking

01:04.500 --> 01:05.250
free world, Mick!

01:05.333 --> 01:06.792
But you guys are gonna
bring me down.

01:06.875 --> 01:08.750
Let me get this straight.

01:08.834 --> 01:10.333
You like
watching Cochran

01:10.417 --> 01:11.792
fuck your wife?

01:11.875 --> 01:13.583
But he's your boss.

01:13.667 --> 01:14.959
How do you put up with that?

01:15.041 --> 01:16.250
You know what, Tom?

01:16.333 --> 01:17.792
We can fix this.

01:19.041 --> 01:21.125
SHORTY: You see
what I'm saying?

01:21.208 --> 01:23.875
We could knock
this place off real easy.

01:24.000 --> 01:25.333
The FBI said that Mickey offered

01:25.417 --> 01:28.542
to get Sully out of the country
as a part of their sting.

01:28.625 --> 01:31.625
Listen to me. You're being
played by Mickey and the FBI.

01:31.709 --> 01:32.792
Yeah.

01:32.875 --> 01:34.500
You ruined my fucking life, Ray.

01:34.583 --> 01:35.667
Okay.

01:35.750 --> 01:36.500
I really liked you.

01:36.583 --> 01:39.041
I trusted you.

01:39.125 --> 01:41.667
Ray.

01:41.750 --> 01:43.417
STEVE:
What's wrong, Ray?

01:43.500 --> 01:44.875
Come in.

01:44.959 --> 01:47.125
Tell me about your day.

02:20.417 --> 02:22.250
(laughs)

02:24.417 --> 02:25.625
Papaya?

02:28.542 --> 02:30.291
Swim?

02:30.375 --> 02:32.542
(groans)

02:32.625 --> 02:35.542
Every day, a man should
tempt the ocean's yin and yang

02:35.625 --> 02:36.959
with his presence.

02:37.041 --> 02:39.208
Let the ocean
decide his fate.

02:41.291 --> 02:44.208
(sighs)

02:44.291 --> 02:45.375
I got to go.

02:47.917 --> 02:51.166
Seems like you could use a day
of quiet reflection, Ray.

02:51.250 --> 02:54.250
All that heavy shit
going on at home.

02:54.333 --> 02:56.375
Your poor daughter's
dead boyfriend.

02:58.125 --> 03:00.041
Your wife...

03:00.125 --> 03:02.250
fucking another man.

03:06.417 --> 03:08.291
I drank too much.

03:08.375 --> 03:10.291
No, don't be like that.

03:10.375 --> 03:12.709
Don't go back
inside your shell.

03:12.792 --> 03:15.959
It's good to talk
to other men about your shit.

03:16.041 --> 03:18.375
It's good to open up.

03:23.792 --> 03:26.625
Hi, Ray.

03:27.792 --> 03:29.875
Bye.

03:36.834 --> 03:40.458
Look at that!

03:40.542 --> 03:43.166
That fucker is back, Ray!

03:43.250 --> 03:45.041
Look at that!
Shit.

03:45.125 --> 03:47.208
Oh, no, don't...

03:47.291 --> 03:49.125
(scoffs)

03:49.208 --> 03:51.083
Motherfucker.

03:56.291 --> 03:59.333
You came back for a beating,
didn't you?

03:59.417 --> 03:59.750
You little fuck!

03:59.834 --> 04:01.959
No! No!

04:02.041 --> 04:03.333
(shouts)

04:03.417 --> 04:04.834
(laughs)

04:06.458 --> 04:08.333
Is this what you want?

04:08.417 --> 04:08.625
No!

04:08.709 --> 04:11.000
Hey!

04:11.083 --> 04:14.542
Come on, Ray! (laughs)

04:14.875 --> 04:17.792
Come on!

04:17.875 --> 04:18.250
(whimpering)

04:18.333 --> 04:20.834
It's your turn!

04:23.500 --> 04:26.667
What are you
fucking doing?!

04:26.750 --> 04:28.917
I get it.

04:29.000 --> 04:30.667
Be merciful.

04:33.166 --> 04:34.667
Get out of here, Bob.

04:34.750 --> 04:36.125
He hits her!

04:36.208 --> 04:37.750
I've seen it!

04:37.834 --> 04:39.333
He hurts her! I
had to protect her!

04:39.417 --> 04:41.792
Get the fuck out of here now!

04:50.041 --> 04:52.750
Once, I was trapped

04:52.834 --> 04:56.792
at the base
of a 12-foot storm wave.

04:56.875 --> 04:59.291
I didn't panic.

04:59.375 --> 05:02.875
I surrendered
to the outcome.

05:02.959 --> 05:06.208
And the loving mother
spit me back out.

05:06.291 --> 05:09.000
Showed me mercy.

05:09.083 --> 05:12.417
Just like you just did
for that poor man.

05:15.166 --> 05:16.375
You hurt Ashley?

05:16.458 --> 05:19.959
That's a part
of our sexual life.

05:20.041 --> 05:22.709
And it's none
of his fucking business.

05:24.166 --> 05:25.875
You lay a finger on her again,
I'll fucking kill you,

05:25.959 --> 05:29.250
you understand me?

05:34.000 --> 05:36.709
Come on, Ray.

05:36.792 --> 05:38.583
Let's go in the water.

05:40.375 --> 05:42.834
Let's let the waves
wash everything away.

05:43.834 --> 05:46.625
Come on.

05:49.333 --> 05:50.667
I'm not fucking swimming
with you!

06:05.834 --> 06:07.750
FLIGHT ATTENDANT:
Ladies and gentlemen,

06:07.834 --> 06:08.834
please stow
all of your belongings

06:08.917 --> 06:11.458
and turn off your portable
electronic devices.

06:11.542 --> 06:14.166
We will be landing
in Los Angeles shortly.

06:14.250 --> 06:15.625
EZRA (over earphones):
...we all were.

06:15.709 --> 06:18.959
Besides, Sean shot the girl
with your gun.

06:19.041 --> 06:20.542
High on your drugs.

06:20.625 --> 06:23.959
Ray said you were
in trouble anyway.

06:24.041 --> 06:25.792
