06:28.750 --> 06:30.208
(sighs)

06:30.291 --> 06:32.333
(recorder clicks)

06:34.208 --> 06:34.917
You need to put that away, miss.

06:35.000 --> 06:37.834
Oh. I'm sorry.

07:15.166 --> 07:16.792
