(panting)

07:17.917 --> 07:20.750
Bridget?

07:22.208 --> 07:25.333
Bridget?! Bridget?

07:27.917 --> 07:29.709
What is it?

07:29.792 --> 07:31.625
(panting)

07:39.834 --> 07:40.750
It's...

07:40.834 --> 07:41.709
(sighs)

07:41.792 --> 07:43.125
Wh-What are you doing?

07:43.208 --> 07:45.291
(panting)

07:47.125 --> 07:48.959
I'm sorry, honey.

07:49.041 --> 07:51.125
It's nothing.

08:01.959 --> 08:05.041
(line ringing)

08:05.125 --> 08:07.250
(phone vibrating)

08:10.166 --> 08:11.208
Kate?

08:11.291 --> 08:11.917
I'm sick of your lies.

08:12.000 --> 08:14.500
Where are you?

08:14.583 --> 08:15.709
Go fuck yourself.

08:21.041 --> 08:23.333
(line ringing)

08:23.417 --> 08:24.959
Yeah.

08:25.041 --> 08:28.583
Avi, I need you to find out
where Kate McPherson is.

08:28.667 --> 08:30.250
Boston?

08:30.333 --> 08:31.375
No, I think she's in L.A.

08:31.458 --> 08:34.083
Boss, I think you should forget
about that woman.

08:34.166 --> 08:36.291
Just fucking find her.

08:38.667 --> 08:39.041
COCHRAN:
Yes, sir.

08:39.125 --> 08:41.750
I understand.

08:41.834 --> 08:43.500
No, no, no.
Thank you, Mr. President.

08:43.583 --> 08:47.917
Yes, sir. I will see you
in Washington.

08:48.000 --> 08:50.125
All right.

08:52.625 --> 08:53.917
Was that...?
Yeah.

08:54.000 --> 08:55.000
Oh. Did you get it?

08:55.083 --> 08:58.166
He said he thought
the people would feel safer

08:58.250 --> 09:00.750
if the country's super cop

09:00.834 --> 09:02.750
was looking after
our nation's security.

09:02.834 --> 09:04.583
(laughs)
(laughs): Oh, my God.

09:04.667 --> 09:07.458
I'm so proud of you.

09:07.542 --> 09:09.125
Washington, here we come.

09:09.208 --> 09:11.500
Mmm.
Mmm.

09:11.583 --> 09:13.834
(chuckles)
Oh, gosh.

09:13.917 --> 09:16.041
I have to lose weight.
No, no.

09:16.125 --> 09:17.083
Yes.
None of that.
You're perfect.

09:17.166 --> 09:19.709
Mwah.

09:19.792 --> 09:22.417
Yes! Yeah!
Oh, my... (gasps)

09:22.500 --> 09:23.625
(exhales)

09:23.709 --> 09:26.625
You know, the vetting process
begins immediately, right?

09:29.291 --> 09:32.583
I know
what we should do tonight.

09:32.667 --> 09:35.166
Celebrate with the Volchecks.

09:37.792 --> 09:40.041
Uh... let me think about that,
okay, sweetie?

09:40.125 --> 09:42.208
Okay.

09:42.291 --> 09:43.917
(kisses)

09:59.917 --> 10:01.959
(chuckling)

10:03.291 --> 10:05.834
Mm-hmm.

10:05.917 --> 10:07.000
(chuckles)

10:07.083 --> 10:11.291
I want to put you all in,
motherfucker.

10:11.375 --> 10:12.083
Not enough.

10:12.166 --> 10:14.542
Not enough chips.

10:14.625 --> 10:15.959
(groans)

10:16.041 --> 10:18.250
Uh...

10:22.583 --> 10:24.667
(sighs)

10:31.208 --> 10:32.709
Okay.

10:35.125 --> 10:37.959
Call.

10:39.625 --> 10:40.875
(chuckles)
Full house.

10:50.291 --> 10:52.333
Four of a kind.

10:52.417 --> 10:54.500
(shouts)

11:05.208 --> 11:05.959
(beeping)

11:09.166 --> 11:11.709
(sighs)
Lord today.

11:11.792 --> 11:12.917
(phone ringing)

11:16.834 --> 11:17.875
What?

11:19.000 --> 11:20.291
Are you with my father?

11:20.375 --> 11:22.208
No, man.
That reporter's back.

11:22.291 --> 11:24.000
I need you with him
all day today.

11:24.083 --> 11:24.625
You don't pay me enough.

11:24.709 --> 11:27.083
Get over there right now.

11:29.208 --> 11:30.583
I need more money.

11:30.667 --> 11:32.000
I can't spend all my time

11:32.083 --> 11:32.959
looking after
that pain in my ass.

11:33.041 --> 11:35.625
You want more money?
Do your fucking job.

11:35.709 --> 11:37.750
Keep my father in check.

11:59.917 --> 12:01.375
Oh, shit.

12:06.208 --> 12:08.625
MICKEY: All the wiring in
that pot place is ancient,

12:08.709 --> 12:09.542
obsolete.

12:09.625 --> 12:11.083
What a fucking break, huh?

12:12.208 --> 12:14.166
That lady reporter is here.

12:14.250 --> 12:16.083
What?
(knocking)

12:16.166 --> 12:19.834
KATE: Mr. Donovan?
It's Kate McPherson.

12:19.917 --> 12:23.291
I forgot to tell you. I gave her
the envelope that you left.

12:23.375 --> 12:25.417
She came back after
the division guys took you.

12:25.500 --> 12:28.583
I thought
you were dead.

12:29.500 --> 12:29.959
Did I fuck up?

12:31.917 --> 12:33.291
It's okay.

12:33.375 --> 12:35.000
No big deal.

12:36.542 --> 12:39.166
Hello, Mr. Donovan.

12:39.250 --> 12:41.000
What brings you
back to town?

12:41.083 --> 12:42.083
You remember Mike Renzetti?

12:42.166 --> 12:45.250
Who?

12:45.333 --> 12:46.667
Come on in.

12:46.750 --> 12:49.083
Mike Renzetti.

12:49.166 --> 12:51.000
Walpole.

12:55.333 --> 12:57.250
Told me Sully hated you.

12:58.417 --> 13:00.542
You go talking to rapists
in Walpole,

13:00.625 --> 13:02.208
you're gonna get wrong ideas.

13:02.291 --> 13:05.166
Told me you ratted out
Sully's entire family.

13:05.250 --> 13:07.125
That he would never
have trusted you

13:07.208 --> 13:10.333
to get him
out of the country.

13:10.417 --> 13:11.917
You want a drink?

13:13.417 --> 13:16.583
Maybe a joint?

13:17.959 --> 13:20.125
What happened to you
the night that you called me?

13:22.083 --> 13:23.375
Nothing.

13:23.458 --> 13:24.542
I showed up the next morning,
your door was busted

13:24.625 --> 13:26.375
and you were gone.

13:26.458 --> 13:28.166
Hmm.

13:28.250 --> 13:29.542
(chuckles)

13:29.625 --> 13:32.583
Somebody scared you.

13:32.667 --> 13:34.959
Then you told me a pack of lies.

13:38.333 --> 13:40.333
Nobody scares me, missy.

13:40.417 --> 13:42.792
Ray does.

13:44.000 --> 13:47.000
Me scared of Ray?
It's the other way around.

13:47.083 --> 13:47.750
No, Ray isn't afraid of anyone.

13:47.834 --> 13:50.208
Oh, yeah?
He's afraid of me.

13:51.125 --> 13:54.625
He paid Sully to...

13:54.709 --> 13:56.125
(chuckles softly)

13:58.250 --> 14:00.208
Paid Sully to do what?

14:00.291 --> 14:02.542
(exhales)

14:02.625 --> 14:03.667
Ask Ray.

14:03.750 --> 14:06.709
Now, get the fuck
out of here.

14:22.834 --> 14:26.458
BRIDGET:
We could have taken the bus.

14:26.542 --> 14:28.583
You both got your phones?

14:28.667 --> 14:30.583
Why don't you loan me your gun?

14:30.667 --> 14:32.583
Don't be a
smart-ass, Bridg.

14:32.667 --> 14:35.125
I'm not comfortable with this.

14:38.041 --> 14:40.291
It's gonna be okay, Mom.

14:40.375 --> 14:41.917
(sighs)

14:43.542 --> 14:46.291
Be careful.

14:53.458 --> 14:55.750
(phone vibrating)

14:57.834 --> 14:59.125
Yeah?

14:59.208 --> 15:00.208
Boss, you were right.

15:00.291 --> 15:03.375
She arrived in L.A. this morning
and rented a car.

15:03.458 --> 15:06.542
Find her.

15:10.583 --> 15:13.000
EZRA: Can I offer you
some water, some juice?

15:13.083 --> 15:14.792
Raymond. We've just
signed over the rights

15:14.875 --> 15:17.542
to Marvin
and Re-Kon's music.

15:17.625 --> 15:19.959
And Mr. Brown
is our new client.

15:20.875 --> 15:22.125
Congratulations.

15:22.208 --> 15:24.542
This means I get access
to him now, right?

15:24.625 --> 15:26.291
LEE:
Of course.

15:26.375 --> 15:29.125
Give me a minute alone
with my nigga.

15:42.709 --> 15:45.583
Hey, look, I hear somebody
might be shopping a video

15:45.667 --> 15:47.375
of whoever killed 'Lil Homie.

15:48.917 --> 15:51.041
Who told you that?

15:51.125 --> 15:53.166
You know the streets, dawg.

15:55.625 --> 15:57.375
I'll look into it.

15:57.458 --> 15:59.750
I'll pay whatever
they want.

15:59.834 --> 16:03.959
I just want to see
whoever hurt my boy get justice.

16:08.291 --> 16:10.667
You and me... we cool?

16:11.625 --> 16:13.417
Sure.

16:29.709 --> 16:30.667
VOLCHECK:
To my mentor...

16:30.750 --> 16:33.667
and good friend.

16:33.750 --> 16:35.750
Here's...

16:35.834 --> 16:38.250
to many years...
of service together.

16:39.917 --> 16:43.417
You can leave
that with me.

16:43.500 --> 16:45.291
No, I'll give it
to him in person.

16:45.375 --> 16:47.750
TRAVIS: "Bathroom on the right"?
Hysterical.

16:47.834 --> 16:50.125
COCHRAN:
I knew another lead singer

16:50.208 --> 16:53.458
who thought that "Purple Haze"
was "'Scuse me while

16:53.542 --> 16:55.542
I kiss this guy."
"Excuse me while

16:55.625 --> 16:58.625
I kiss this guy"?
Not "kiss the sky,"
"kiss this guy."

16:58.709 --> 17:00.166
(laughs):
That is hysterical.

17:00.250 --> 17:01.750
I'm sorry
to interrupt.

17:01.834 --> 17:02.917
Hi, Tom.

17:03.000 --> 17:04.250
Travis was just leaving.

17:04.792 --> 17:07.041
Thank you, Travis.

17:07.125 --> 17:12.500
Sir, can I just say
how proud I am of you.

17:12.583 --> 17:13.834
Tommy, what
do you want?

17:13.917 --> 17:16.709
Well, I just...
wanted to know

17:16.792 --> 17:18.834
if I was going
to Washington with you.

17:20.333 --> 17:23.083
I don't think so, Tom, no.

17:28.208 --> 17:31.625
Well, then would you consider me
as your replacement here?

17:31.709 --> 17:32.834
Wow. (chuckles)

17:32.917 --> 17:35.125
My replacement, huh?

17:35.208 --> 17:37.792
That's what all this has
been about for you, huh?

17:37.875 --> 17:39.625
Just, uh, moving on
up in your career?

17:39.709 --> 17:40.792
No, of course not, sir.

17:40.875 --> 17:44.667
It's just that you've been
a mentor to me, and a guide,

17:44.750 --> 17:46.709
and I have the utmost
respect for you.

17:46.792 --> 17:48.542
And I thought since

17:48.625 --> 17:50.917
there was a position opening up
here now that maybe...

17:51.000 --> 17:52.917
You thought you'd just
slide on in there, huh?

17:53.000 --> 17:55.041
Of-of course not... sir.

17:55.125 --> 17:57.959
It's just... we've
all been so close...

17:58.041 --> 17:59.959
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

18:00.041 --> 18:02.291
Are you blackmailing
me, Tom?

18:02.375 --> 18:03.959
No.

18:04.041 --> 18:05.250
Are you sure?

18:05.333 --> 18:05.792
Yes, sir. Not at all.

18:05.875 --> 18:08.750
No. Sir, I'm just...

18:08.834 --> 18:11.041
Congratulations.

18:11.125 --> 18:13.959
You deserve it.

18:19.417 --> 18:21.000
I'm looking over everything.

18:21.083 --> 18:23.041
Everybody's got their job.

18:23.125 --> 18:25.959
And timing is important,
so you're important.

18:26.041 --> 18:27.250
I got this, Mick.

18:27.333 --> 18:29.333
I can blow that security guard
in two minutes,

18:29.417 --> 18:30.125
or I can blow him in ten.

18:30.208 --> 18:31.542
Make it go as
long as you can.

18:31.625 --> 18:33.625
Use your wiles.

18:33.709 --> 18:34.834
I won't tickle his balls, then.

18:34.917 --> 18:36.709
No finger up the ass.

18:36.792 --> 18:38.875
Oh, thank you for that.

18:38.959 --> 18:41.667
Guys... I don't think
you understand.

18:41.750 --> 18:45.333
I need two and a half hours
just to crack the safe.

18:45.417 --> 18:46.500
You're gonna get your time.

18:46.583 --> 18:48.500
This is just to get us in there
and hide.

18:48.583 --> 18:51.583
But we still need to go in
through the roof.

18:51.667 --> 18:53.667
Really? Why?

18:53.750 --> 18:55.750
