door, there could be an alarm.

18:55.834 --> 18:57.000
No.

18:57.083 --> 18:59.834
They never put an alarm
on the roof. (coughing)

18:59.917 --> 19:01.917
We should tunnel in
throh the fucking floor.

19:02.000 --> 19:04.500
That'll only take us
a year and a half.

19:04.583 --> 19:05.333
(coughing continues)

19:09.458 --> 19:10.583
Are you all right?

19:10.667 --> 19:12.750
I'm fine, Mick.

19:12.834 --> 19:13.542
Seriously, I'm fine.

19:13.625 --> 19:15.875
