39:23.583 --> 39:25.000
(sighs)

39:28.000 --> 39:30.792
You know I'd never let anything
happen to you or the kids.

39:36.583 --> 39:38.500
(phone vibrating)

39:43.917 --> 39:45.125
Yeah?

39:45.208 --> 39:45.625
I know where she is.

39:49.166 --> 39:51.583
(sighs)

40:03.458 --> 40:04.625
Are you coming
back, Daddy?

40:07.625 --> 40:09.583
