to come looking for you?

40:45.542 --> 40:46.792
(sniffles)

40:50.583 --> 40:52.709
Half now, half later.

40:55.417 --> 40:59.000
Like I said,
tomorrow or the next day,

40:59.083 --> 41:02.041
I tell you to turn me off,
you turn me off.

41:03.417 --> 41:06.250
What do you
got planned?

41:06.333 --> 41:09.375
You got your money.
No questions.

41:09.458 --> 41:14.208
Look, all I'm saying is, what
if I wanted more than $5,000?

41:14.291 --> 41:16.458
What would I have to do?

41:17.583 --> 41:20.417
Ooh.

41:22.750 --> 41:24.583
Okay.

41:58.667 --> 42:00.208
