Why?

42:11.667 --> 42:12.875
To keep you alive.

42:12.959 --> 42:15.625
Bullshit. You didn't want
to go to fucking prison.

42:19.792 --> 42:21.125
(sighs)

42:21.208 --> 42:23.500
You keep this up,
you're gonna end up dead, Kate.

42:23.583 --> 42:25.625
