42:25.709 --> 42:28.166
Journalists die all the time--
occupational hazard.

42:29.792 --> 42:34.291
You want to tell me
why you paid two million dollars

42:34.375 --> 42:36.291
to have Sully
kill your father?

42:43.542 --> 42:45.583
You don't quit, do you?

42:45.667 --> 42:47.458
No.

42:47.542 --> 42:49.375
What'd you get for dinner?

42:52.709 --> 42:55.250
Burger. Want half?

42:55.333 --> 42:57.834
Yeah, sure. Fucking starving.

43:04.375 --> 43:06.500
Thanks.

43:14.250 --> 43:16.542
So, why do you hate
your dad so much?

43:16.625 --> 43:17.750
What'd he do?

43:23.542 --> 43:25.083
He was supposed to take me
to a baseball game.

43:25.166 --> 43:28.041
Never showed up.

43:28.125 --> 43:29.834
Come on, Ray.

43:29.917 --> 43:31.792
I'm serious.

43:34.834 --> 43:37.208
I know that Sean Walker
killed that girl,

43:37.291 --> 43:39.083
and that you
framed him for it.

43:39.166 --> 43:41.041
Why?

43:48.250 --> 43:50.125
All right, fuck it.

43:50.208 --> 43:52.875
My father was Sean's dealer.

43:52.959 --> 43:54.500
Sean got high,

43:54.583 --> 43:56.208
Mickey let him play
with his gun.

43:56.291 --> 44:00.083
Fucking idiot thought
it was a toy, fired it,

44:00.166 --> 44:02.291
that was the end of Colleen.

44:02.375 --> 44:04.542
So, you blame
Mickey for that?

44:04.625 --> 44:05.291
Yeah, I fucking blame him.

44:05.375 --> 44:07.041
Everything he touches

44:07.125 --> 44:09.542
turns to shit.

44:09.625 --> 44:12.041
My mother's dying of cancer,
my sister's using.

44:12.125 --> 44:13.834
Finally, she throws herself
off a roof.

44:13.917 --> 44:16.542
Where the fuck was he?

44:16.625 --> 44:17.709
Getting high.

44:17.792 --> 44:22.083
Screwing some whore
in the projects.

44:22.166 --> 44:23.667
(sighs)

44:25.792 --> 44:27.917
I did some research.

44:36.583 --> 44:39.667
The day your father
gets out of prison,

44:39.750 --> 44:41.291
the priest was shot.

44:41.375 --> 44:44.333
St. Josephine's Parish.

44:47.709 --> 44:49.250
(sighs)

44:49.333 --> 44:52.750
I know about your brother
Brendan's settlement.

44:52.834 --> 44:54.750
$1.4 million.

44:54.834 --> 44:55.917
Oh, yeah?

44:58.458 --> 45:00.375
