like yours.

45:03.667 --> 45:06.000
The mother's sick,
the father's absent.

45:15.875 --> 45:18.250
What about Terry?

45:20.375 --> 45:21.375
Did that priest abuse him, too?

45:21.458 --> 45:24.333
Leave Terry out of it.

45:24.417 --> 45:27.291
They don't stop at one kid.

45:27.375 --> 45:29.208
They move from one
to the other.

45:29.291 --> 45:31.166
