45:31.250 --> 45:33.500
(gasps)

45:36.500 --> 45:38.583
(Kate moaning)

45:57.000 --> 45:58.083
(panting)

46:02.250 --> 46:04.125
(groans softly)

46:08.500 --> 46:10.583
(moaning)

46:22.500 --> 46:24.166
Did he get you, too?

46:24.250 --> 46:28.333
Shut up.

46:28.417 --> 46:30.834
Did he fuck you up
like he fucked up your brother?

46:30.917 --> 46:32.041
(gasps)

46:36.125 --> 46:37.333
(groans)

46:37.417 --> 46:38.750
(shrieks)

46:38.834 --> 46:39.959
(both grunting)

46:43.458 --> 46:46.291
(crying)

46:46.375 --> 46:47.709
Ray!

46:47.792 --> 46:48.917
(grunting)

46:50.875 --> 46:53.709
(gasping)

46:53.792 --> 46:56.166
(coughing)
(sighs)

46:58.208 --> 47:00.291
